-- Steinhoff International Rated `Overweight' in New Morgan Stanley Coverage
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-12-01T08:52:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-01/steinhoff-international-rated-overweight-in-new-morgan-stanley-coverage.html
Steinhoff International Holdings
Ltd., Africa’s largest furniture maker, was rated “overweight”
in new coverage at RMB Morgan Stanley.  “Steinhoff enjoys a competitive advantage over smaller
competitors given its vertically integrated business model,
integrated logistics, scale advantages and alignment of strong
partners,” RMB Morgan Stanley analysts Danie Pretorius and
Qaqambile Dwayi said in a note to clients today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  